James Knight (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Knight_(actor) 0 James Knight (4 May 1891 in Canterbury, Kent – 1948 in Gloucestershire) was a British actor. Starting as a wrestler, he became a leading man in British silent films, and later a character actor in smaller film roles.
